{"tid":265891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"＄5食 「 巨星雪條 」 ！ 手工雪條店Stickhouse重製懷舊雪條","createTime":"2017-06-01T04:55:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-01T06:59:28.000Z","uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"78a9b1a6229d43dc787ebd57765ee4e9d00b0a2b","tid":265891,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T04:55:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.weekendhk.com/dining/%E5%85%92%E7%AB%A5%E7%AF%80-%E5%B7%A8%E6%98%9F%E9%9B%AA%E6%A2%9D-stickhouse/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.weekendhk.com%2Fdining%2F%25E5%2585%2592%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E7%25AF%2580-%25E5%25B7%25A8%25E6%2598%259F%25E9%259B%25AA%25E6%25A2%259D-stickhouse%2F&d=tdfcCaI%2BvaIn3erCU8nExIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=5e2801d9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.weekendhk.com/dining/%E5%85%92%E7%AB%A5%E7%AF%80-%E5%B7%A8%E6%98%9F%E9%9B%AA%E6%A2%9D-stickhouse/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/icecream-feature_871313633592ec520127c6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.weekendhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2Ficecream-feature_871313633592ec520127c6.jpg&h=28f2fdbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n夏天來臨，又有藉口食雪條！提起雪條，相信很多人都非常懷念穿梭機、檸檬茶味、藍戰士、巨星等絕版懷舊雪條，希望嘉頓可以重出這些雪條，雖然未等到，但現在也有機會食到巨星雪條喇！意大利手工雪條店Stickhouse新推出懷舊雪條系列，有 「 巨星雪條 」 及「木瓜奶雪條」兩款經典口味，開售首天（6月1日）更可以 $5 懷舊價就食到，趁着國際兒童節，帶埋小朋友去試下這款懷舊的味道啦～<br />\n撰文、攝影：Hailey<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/iceceam9_1222807123592ec324e5798.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.weekendhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2Ficeceam9_1222807123592ec324e5798.jpg&h=0e2ed90f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/iceceam11_994535924592ec328f39b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.weekendhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2Ficeceam11_994535924592ec328f39b2.jpg&h=23a7cb63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/iceceam10_366985739592ec3273a8be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.weekendhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2Ficeceam10_366985739592ec3273a8be.jpg&h=b6a73105&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1418de822f90f3f6c2d66d3dee76ddfcd1da6573","tid":265891,"uid":35814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T04:59:08.000Z","msg":"支巨星個樣好求其喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果嘉頓仲有出呢幾隻經典<br />\n唔知今時今日咩價位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：第一次買仲係$1.5一支，最後好似要$3"},{"pid":"4cfbc7698f492ebd0cc0b943e1b02b747e18378d","tid":265891,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T05:00:09.000Z","msg":"本來想試下，但新假期推介，不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93574bcc7a2beb5fbd7530c6f8a1cda7889cc44d","tid":265891,"uid":75300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T05:00:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支巨星個樣好求其喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果嘉頓仲有出呢幾隻經典<br />\n唔知今時今日咩價位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：第一次買仲係$1.5一支，最後好似要$3</blockquote><br />\n五蚊枝係限量，好似首廿幾支先五蚊，之後$48 一枝"},{"pid":"8626e9a301e114d01d35c71e1ed93834dae3b116","tid":265891,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T05:01:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>支巨星個樣好求其喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果嘉頓仲有出呢幾隻經典<br />\n唔知今時今日咩價位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：第一次買仲係$1.5一支，最後好似要$3</blockquote><br />\n五蚊枝係限量，好似首廿幾支先五蚊，之後$48 一枝</blockquote><br />\n48<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0932dad4d908ad2e72cc6341839983bcab595